Stéphane Freiss https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/St%C3%A9phane_Freiss 0 Stéphane Freiss (born 22 November 1960) is a French film, television, and stage actor. He won a César Award for his performance in the 1988 film Chouans!. Stéphane_Freiss ( born 22_November_1960 ) is a_French_film , television , and stage_actor .
